      <th style="padding:14px; border:1px solid #cc0000;">Supports Voter ID?</th>
      <th style="padding:14px; border:1px solid #cc0000;">Last Action Taken</th>
      <th style="padding:14px; border:1px solid #cc0000;">Status</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr style="background-color:#fff;">
      <td style="padding:12px; border:1px solid #cc0000;">President Trump</td>
      <td style="padding:12px; border:1px solid #cc0000;">✅ YES</td>
