      <td style="padding:12px; border:1px solid #cc0000; color:#cc0000;">❌ Not Yet</td>
      <td style="padding:12px; border:1px solid #cc0000;">No action on file</td>
      <td style="padding:12px; border:1px solid #cc0000; font-weight:bold; color:#cc0000;">Unconfirmed!
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td colspan="4" style="text-align:center; padding:20px 12px; background-color:#ffffff; border:1px solid #cc0000;">
        <a href="{{LINK}}" style="background-color:#cc0000; color:#ffffff; padding:12px 24px; text-decoration:none; font-weight:bold; border-radius:5px; display:inline-block;">
          ✅ Fix Your Record Now
